---
title: Spanish Cod & Chorizo with Crispy Oregano Potatoes & Sautéed Kale
description: Preheat oven to 400 degrees. Cut the potatoes into 1/2-inch pieces. Finely chop the oregano leaves. On a baking sheet, toss the potatoes with the oregano, 1 tablespoon olive oil, and a pinch of salt and pepper. Place the baking sheet in the oven and roast for about 15-20 minutes, until golden brown.
